3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes an automated method for lesion segmentation, which is a common application of artificial intelligence.
4. cs.MS (Medical Imaging) - The paper focuses on breast cancer diagnosis using ultrasound imaging, which is a subfield of medical imaging.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with the segmentation of images, which is a multimedia-related task.
